    "description": "<p>You place a magical mark on a creature or yourself granting&nbsp;power to fight and win against your foes.</p>\n<p>When you cast this spell, the target gains 4 points or exertion, may remove a level of fatigue or strife, and gains 20 temporary hit points.</p>\n<p>In addition, while the mark remains visible, the target sheds dim light in a 5-foot area, gains a +2 bonus to AC, has an expertise die on Intimidation checks, and their weapon attacks deal an additional 1d4 points of radiant damage.</p>",
